verbose_text: Compared with model group, the SOD level in 20 mg/kg icariside II group and GSH-Px and catalase levels in 10 and 20 mg/kg icariside II groups were significantly increased, respectively (P < 0.05), and the MDA level in 5, 10 and 20 mg/kg icariside II groups was significantly decreased, respectively (P < 0.05) (XREF_TABLE).
